jection and interactive advertising. I recently interviewed him on how TMM came to be, where it’s headed and his (and everyone at TMM) passion for cars.'),(230,102,'_summary','field_4f52f5c0b695a'),(231,102,'recommended_links','4'),(232,102,'_recommended_links','field_4f52f8762087b'),(233,102,'state','active'),(234,102,'_state','field_4f52f8ae74b69'),(235,102,'feature_image','163'),(236,102,'_feature_image','field_4f52fa7e37fbf'),(237,103,'_edit_last','2'),(238,103,'_edit_lock','1333754199:1'),(239,103,'interviewee_title','Founder & CEO of JP Logistics Inc.'),(240,103,'_interviewee_title','field_4f52f4ea9f5fb'),(241,103,'summary','JP Logistics specializes in global auto transport based out of Sun Valley, CA. They offer domestic transport and international shipping for some of the most expensive and rare cars in the world. JP logistics has a level of expertise and service that has earned them corporate contracts with Lamborghini, Bentley, Rolls Royce, Bugatti and more. George Sukunyan is the CEO and founder of this successful company. I recently had the chance to interview him to discuss business, cars, the perks of the job and some of the well-known people he has had the opportunity to meet and work with.'),(242,103,'_summary','field_4f52f5c0b695a'),(243,103,'recommended_links','1'),(244,103,'_recommended_links','field_4f52f8762087b'),(245,103,'state','active'),(246,103,'_state','field_4f52f8ae74b69'),(247,103,'feature_image','162'),(248,103,'_feature_image','field_4f52fa7e37fbf'),(249,104,'_edit_last','2'),(250,104,'_edit_lock','1333657336:2'),(251,104,'interviewee_title','Artist'),(252,104,'_interviewee_title','field_4f52f4ea9f5fb'),(253,104,'summary',''),(254,104,'_summary','field_4f52f5c0b695a'),(255,104,'recommended_links','0'),(256,104,'_recommended_links','field_4f52f8762087b'),(257,104,'state','upcoming'),(258,104,'_state','field_4f52f8ae74b69'),(259,104,'feature_image','150'),(260,104,'_feature_image','field_4f52fa7e37fbf'),(261,105,'_wp_attached_file','201