 on a roll of black and white back in Sydney.\n\nSo now we\'ve just begun posting one day at a time - him in Sydney, me in New York - and we\'ve called it <a title=\"35mm Postcards\" href=\"http://www.35mmPostcards.tumblr.com\" target=\"_blank\">35mm Postcards</a>. First up is the month of December, leading up to Christmas. Its super simple, just a way of saying \"hello\" and the tangible nature of film is a little like a postcard instead of an email I guess. Its been an amazing exercise in slowing down and being extremely decisive and disciplined in what I choose to shoot.\n<h3 class=\"question clear-left\">Asher:</h3>\nWhat are some of the best things about being a photographer?\n<h3 class=\"answer\">Glen:</h3>\n<p class=\"spacer\">Shooting. I just love shooting. Some days I love it because of the people I meet, some days its the opportunity to shoot something ridiculously amazing, other days I just like the feel of the shutter under my finger, other days its the delayed gratification of not knowing what the picture\'s going to look like until I take another 35 shots to finish the roll and then get it developed. I love it all and wouldn\'t trade it for anything.</p>','Glen Allsop','','inherit','open','open','','72-autosave','','','2012-04-06 03:51:13','2012-04-06 10:51:13','',72,'http://spiraldesign.ca/72-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(132,1,'2012-03-10 23:35:20','2012-03-10 23:35:20','','Interview Custom Fields','','inherit','open','open','','acf_interview-custom-fields-13','','','2012-03-10 23:35:20','2012-03-10 23:35:20','',31,'http://spiraldesign.ca/acf_interview-custom-fields-13/',0,'revision','',0),(121,1,'2012-03-08 06:00:41','2012-03-08 06:00:41','','interview-image-1','','inherit','open','open','','interview-image-1','','','2012-03-08 06:00:41','2012-03-08 06:00:41','',72,'http://spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/interview-image-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(131,1,'2012-03-10 23:29:50','2012-03-10 23:29:50','','Interview Custom Fields','